Name: Anfield Energy Inc.
Description: Anfield Energy Inc. (AEC) is a real estate investment trust (REIT) specializing in the acquisition, management, and development of multifamily residential properties across the United States. The company focuses on strategically investing in high-quality assets situated in prime markets, with an emphasis on enhancing property value through superior management practices and strategic renovations. AEC's diversified portfolio includes both luxury and affordable housing options, designed to meet the needs of a broad demographic spectrum. By leveraging in-depth market analytics and a robust operational framework, AEC aims to achieve sustainable growth and deliver attractive returns to its investors.
